#

Tandoori Chicken Skewers with Spicy Yogurt Sauce and Cilantro Rice

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Indian CuisineGrilledSkewersSpicy

Description

Juicy tandoori chicken skewers paired with a zesty yogurt sauce and fragrant cilantro rice.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breasts: 1 lb
  • Tandoori spice mix: 2 tbsp
  • Plain yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Basmati rice: 1 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Red chili powder: 1 tsp
  • Green chili: 1, minced
